<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="References">References</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Incarceration_in_the_United_States&amp;action=edit&amp;section=51" title="Edit section: References"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
