ink%2C+Nathan+W.&amp;rft_id=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fpii%2FS0277953619306136&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AIncarceration+in+the+United+States" class="Z3988"></span></span>
